<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1935-09-03T18:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1935-09-03T18:00:00-05:00" n="70" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d70">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">500.A15A4 Personnel/1464:
                                Telegram</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss>
                                    to the American Delegate</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Wilson</hi></persName>)</head>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#center">[Extract]</seg>
                            </opener>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1935-09-03T19:00:00-04:00">September 3, 1935—7 p.m.</date>
                                </dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>500. Your 1054, September 2, 6 p.m. You are instructed to release
                                quarters now occupied by Disarmament Delegation about first of
                                October or upon termination of next Bureau meeting, unless in your
                                judgment the situation subsequent to that date would require you to
                                maintain the office for a brief period longer. Quarters will be
                                obtained in building occupied by Consulate.<note n="92" xml:id="d70fn92">In telegram No. 1062, October 30, 1935, noon,
                                    the American delegate reported the change of office had been
                                    effected (500.A15A4 Personnel/1488).</note>
                            </p>
                            <p rend="center">. . . . . . . . . . . . . .</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>